# Volikos
A tiny, intro-friendly LLVM language.

## Installation
### Prerequisites
* Python 3.8+ or pipx
* LLVM/Clang (installed via your system package manager)

### Install via pipx
```bash
pipx install volikos
```

### Install via pip
```bash
pip install volikos
```

### Verify
```bash
volikos --help
```
